<div style="width: 52px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ambox_style.png" class="image" title="Ambox style.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d6/Ambox_style.png" width="40" height="40" border="0" /></a></div>
</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article's <b>introduction may be too long</b>. Please help by moving some material from it into the body of the article. Read the <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Guide_to_layout" title="Wikipedia:Guide to layout" class="mw-redirect">layout guide</a> and Wikipedia's <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Lead_section" title="Wikipedia:Lead section">lead section guidelines</a> for more information. Discuss this issue on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Solar_hot_water" title="Talk:Solar hot water">talk page</a>. <small><i>(November 2008)</i></small></td>
